THE MOST DIRECT PATH TO YOUR DEGREE


































No matter where you want to go in nursing, Capella has an accredited online degree program that will provide the most direct path to your goals. Potentially save time and money and earn your degree in a more efficient way with unique pathways such as our BSN-to-DNP, RN-to-MSN, RN-to-BSN/MSN, and more.


















AFFORDABLE
TUITION


































Nursing Scholarships Available: Save up to $5,000*. Start your degree program and apply for a scholarship. Plus, employer, military, and nursing association discounts can make your degree even more affordable.




















APPLY PREVIOUS
 KNOWLEDGE

































Potentially reduce the time and cost of finishing your degree by maximizing your transfer credits from previous work (up to 75% of your program for BSN). You can also earn credits through our Prior Learning Assessment process by demonstrating mastery of competencies, and applying credentials like your CNML, CPHIMS, or ANCC RN-BC Informatics certification. 



















*MSN FlexPath option is not eligible.





















 
FlexPath: Your Degree. Your Pace.
As a nurse, you've got a lot on our plate. School is a priority, but in reality, family and work come first. With FlexPath, you can still build the career-advancing skills and knowledge you need, but with a class schedule entirely controlled by you. Earn your RN-to-BSN or MSN degree on your schedule.




































 

SELF-PACED: Once you complete a course, whether that takes you two weeks or 12, you're free to move on to the next course without having to wait for a new term to begin.

PACE DETERMINES PRICE: You can complete as many courses as you want, up to two simultaneously, each quarter for one flat tuition fee*. The faster your pace, the more money you may save.

LEVERAGE WHAT YOU KNOW: Because you already have a lot of knowledge and experience, you can move faster through what you know and take your time on what you need to learn.

SUPPORT AT EVERY LEVEL: From start to finish you'll have learning support from tutors, detailed feedback from faculty, and personalized planning from coaches.


* Books, supplies, and other fees may apply.































ACCREDITED AND RESPECTED













 
 The BSN, MSN, and DNP degree programs at Capella University are accredited by the Commission on Collegiate Nursing Education (CCNE) (http://www.aacn.nche.edu/ccne-accreditation). Accreditation by CCNE serves as a statement of good educational practice in the field of nursing. CCNE is a nationally recognized accrediting agency approved by the U.S. Secretary of Education.
















